Template: cert-agent/redis-url
Type: string
Default: redis://localhost:6379
Description: Redis connection URL:
 Please enter the Redis connection URL for cert-agent.
 .
 The URL should be in the format: redis://[username:password@]host:port[/database]
 Examples:
  - redis://localhost:6379 (default)
  - redis://user:pass@redis.example.com:6380/0
  - redis://redis-server:6379

Template: cert-agent/redis-port
Type: string
Default: 6379
Description: Redis port:
 Please enter the Redis port number.
 .
 Default is 6379. If you're using a non-standard port, enter it here.

Template: cert-agent/grpc-port
Type: string
Default: 50051
Description: gRPC server port:
 Please enter the port number for the gRPC server.
 .
 Default is 50051. Choose a port that's not in use by other services.

Template: cert-agent/enable-service
Type: boolean
Default: true
Description: Enable cert-agent service:
 Do you want to enable and start the cert-agent service automatically?
 .
 If enabled, the service will start automatically on boot and after installation.
